<header id="content-header" class="container-sm article-header md:text-center mb-2 md:mb-4">
<h1 class="font-featured italic text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight tracking-wide">Why Microsoft Flight Simulator 2020 Is This Year&#039;s Most Ambitious Game</h1>
<p class="font-brand mb-4 leading-normal">Are you ready for AI-powered gaming? Microsoft Flight Simulator 2020 is the newest iteration of the popular simulation series, but advances in technology show us what&#039;s ahead for the world of video games.</p>
</header>
<div class="container mb-6 text-sm flex flex-wrap md:justify-center md:items-center">
<div class="w-full md:w-auto inline-block flex items-center">
<a href="/authors/k-thor-jensen" data-module="author-byline" data-item="author-list" data-element="author-image" data-position="1" x-track-ga-click>
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-full mr-2 hidden lg:inline-block" style="height:50px; width: 50px;">
<img src="https://i.pcmag.com/imagery/authors/03u6fS0y2ePDnkUA7zSb3ef.1560221536.fit_lim.size_100x100.jpg" alt="K. Thor Jensen" width="50px" height="50px">
</div>
</a>
<span class="font-brand font-semibold leading-tight">
By
<a href="/authors/k-thor-jensen" class="font-brand font-semibold leading-tight underline" data-module="author-byline" data-item="author-list" data-element="author-name" data-position="1" x-track-ga-click>K. Thor Jensen</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-auto flex items-center justify-between inline-block md:justify-center">
<div class="font-brand md:ml-4">
