nd airports are locked behind Flight Simulator&#039;s &quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;$89.99 Deluxe Bundle&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;marks&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;link&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/zdcs.link\/OKOR7&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:null}}]},{&quot;text&quot;:&quot; and &quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;$119 Premium Deluxe Bundle&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;marks&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;link&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/zdcs.link\/5doY8&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:null}}]},{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;, but, hey, what do I know? Perhaps brokering licensing deals with Boeing and Textron doesn&#039;t come cheap.&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}]},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;paragraph&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:[{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Still, Microsoft Flight Simulator delivers a much-needed chill, exploratory vibe, regardless of your favored tier. During a time when many people are encouraged to stay at home or social distance, and when self-serving or flat-out numskull representatives seemingly make all the wrong decisions, it&#039;s pure escapism to gently push the throttle and see what&#039;s over the horizon.&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}]},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;mashable_video&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;63nwkYXDn5&quot;}}]},&quot;images&quot;:{&quot;autoincrement&quot;:9,&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;index&quot;:1,&quot;path&quot;:&quot;articles\/05PkcvCkhgqwVpN4bmSg2sm-1.jpg&quot;,&quot;extension&quot;:&quot;jpg&quot;,&quot;animated&quot;:false,&quot;width&quot;:1920,&quot;height&quot;:1080,&quot;hash&quot;:&quot;6407e2969c9605f1dde0e3974309fb53&quot;,&quot;timestamp&quot;:1597438531,&quot;metadata&quot;:[]},{&quot;index&quot;:2,&quot;path&quot;:&quot;articles\/05PkcvCkhgqwVpN4bmSg2sm-2.png&quot;,&quot;extension&quot;:&quot;png&quot;,&quot;animated&quot;:false,