<h3 class="text-2xl font-brand font-bold">About K. Thor Jensen</h3>
<div class="mb-12">
<div class="mb-8">
<a href="/authors/k-thor-jensen" class="inline-block float-left mr-2 mt-2">
<img src="https://i.pcmag.com/imagery/authors/03u6fS0y2ePDnkUA7zSb3ef.1560221536.fit_lim.size_100x100.jpg" alt="K. Thor Jensen" width="50px" height="50px" class="mr-2 rounded-full">
</a>
<div class="author-bio mt-2 leading-loose lg:text-lg"><div>K. Thor Jensen is a writer and cartoonist living in the Pacific Northwest. He has contributed to dozens of prestigious outlets, including PCMag, Tested, Clickhole, and Newsweek. His second graphic novel, <a href="https://zdcs.link/2kdBW" target="_blank"><em>Cloud Stories</em></a>, was released in 2017. </div></div>
</div>
